f
a
\lim_{\alpha\to a}f(\alpha)=f(a) \iff \lim_{h\to 0}f(a+h)-f(a)=0 \iff \lim_{h\to 0}\vert\vert f(a+h)-f(a)\vert\vert=0
\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{f(a+h)-f(a)-Df(a)h}{\vert\vert h\vert\vert}=0
\vert\vert f(a+h)-f(a)\vert\vert \le\vert\vert f(a+h)-f(a)-Df(a)h\vert\vert +\vert\vert Df(a)h\vert\vert =\frac{\vert\vert f(a+h)-f(a)-Df(a)h}{\vert\vert h\vert\vert}\cdot \vert\vert h\vert\vert+\vert\vert Df(a)h\vert\vert\to 0.0=0
